{"tid":1012103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌市中心再淪陷    東薈城食肆人龍處處居民叫苦","createTime":"2019-02-07T10:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T04:45:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":192,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"ca34bc47df8f17f559fe23228405e4ea0dea7a2a","tid":1012103,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190207/large/1549532793_f473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190207%2Flarge%2F1549532793_f473.jpg&h=96aa1899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東涌市中心東薈城一帶今午幾乎所有食肆都排長龍。(fb東涌居民關注組)<br />\n<br />\n今日大年初三有大量內地團友及自由行旅客經港珠澳大橋來港後，選擇乘車到鄰近的東薈城商場購物及飲食，令東涌市中心再次人頭湧湧。據facebook「東涌居民關注組」上載的照片及帖文，今日下午約二時，東薈城可謂「人山人海」，基本所有食肆包括連鎖快餐店在內均大排長龍，部分食肆有逾30人排隊輪候。<br />\n<br />\n即使是商場內的便利店、又或是商場外以外賣為主的食肆，一樣出現小人龍，有居民嘆「搵食」艱難。<br />\n<br />\n有商戶則慨嘆旅客人流來得太遲，因早前在區內舉行的東涌年宵市集，人流少得可憐，不少年宵攤檔營運者遂蒙受損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190207/59232978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190207%2F59232978&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BciL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=5a13ff94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190207%2F59232978&h=378a2097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190207/59232978</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190207/large/1549532793_3974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190207%2Flarge%2F1549532793_3974.jpg&h=6078eb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190207/large/1549532793_4635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190207%2Flarge%2F1549532793_4635.jpg&h=290ef4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190207/large/1549532797_eb25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190207%2Flarge%2F1549532797_eb25.jpg&h=f703aec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc0cbf3f275ce1f4e7054beaf9d6002b90b0e6d2","tid":1012103,"uid":89037,"like":160,"dislike":1,"score":159,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"包容下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d13102a931ff54ebfd13fad4e97f130785d353","tid":1012103,"uid":216642,"like":132,"dislike":3,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"有流感病毒嘅病患者幫幫手響果度行返轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55faf787a1e1b7fa3471231cca6a9ea0098b3dc","tid":1012103,"uid":64345,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"東涌 - 站在中港旅遊產業的最前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6462019587f3f9935c8e8eeb24b9cace82f642","tid":1012103,"uid":228143,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"真心問起果到做生意咪賺勁多?"},{"pid":"76fc7ba1372a274dcd044723935b0cfd748d5dd8","tid":1012103,"uid":25822,"like":120,"dislike":8,"score":112,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"當年光復屯門上水，東涌班居民去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8869218745fb8e889ac2e2999fa8a2bd74a74c5","tid":1012103,"uid":19552,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"8e6462019587f3f9935c8e8eeb24b9cace82f642","tid":1012103,"uid":228143,"like":41,"dislik